# White Paper and Specification Folders

## Purpose

The repository separates conceptual documentation from normative technical specifications.

This distinction preserves a clear boundary between explanatory materials (the White Paper) and implementation-oriented governance specifications (the Specification Library).

The **White Paper** explains *why* the Elastic Governance Layer (EGL) is needed and establishes its theoretical, legal, and institutional foundations.

The **Specification** documents define *how* EGL is structured and how its governance components can be consistently implemented, assessed, audited, and extended.

